{"tid":1055730,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點先知自己鐘意一個人","createTime":"2019-03-10T17:26:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T17:56:32.000Z","uid":225437,"like":72,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"0406030df26744e865c3fd94960664b3a92adfe8","tid":1055730,"uid":225437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T17:26:23.000Z","msg":"真係愛嗰種既鐘意<br />\n有時過電都唔肯定自己係唔係鐘意人<br />\n有時追女神又唔肯定自己係唔係鐘意佢<br />\n拍拖到散回頭都唔肯定自己有冇鐘意過人<br />\n點樣先知自己有冇鐘意一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b3f83b6c4f28d8bf73cd90392d945f86deb8e0a","tid":1055730,"uid":197743,"like":27,"dislike":3,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T17:28:37.000Z","msg":"有心動嘅感覺我已經會當係中意"},{"pid":"81cce03ac0336fc05ce51cc6b2a9df9fdd9344f1","tid":1055730,"uid":21355,"like":76,"dislike":2,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T17:29:11.000Z","msg":"成日諗佢想見佢"},{"pid":"294bfb19dafad8b4485a87eb57667da6002d9cae","tid":1055730,"uid":38907,"like":95,"dislike":4,"score":91,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T17:31:45.000Z","msg":"咩都想同佢分享<br />\n見到咩想食/邊度好玩/有咩開心唔開心頹嬲<br />\n都想同佢講"},{"pid":"f31fa46e0e9f8f07ba98878ca90775085b4b2b84","tid":1055730,"uid":215601,"like":57,"dislike":2,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T17:32:39.000Z","msg":"知道佢鍾意第二個會唔開心"},{"pid":"72e7ca4e74631ef1be79cd44401d0f1b6c50b4ee","tid":1055730,"uid":202425,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T17:33:58.000Z","msg":"成日諗起佢"},{"pid":"618fa5e52afb0d689e8318bea955cdb8d4fb1a97","tid":1055730,"uid":179844,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T17:34:44.000Z","msg":"想以後都係度陪住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc7acc68afb252d1f2732bb54922d8d8ebabffae","tid":1055730,"uid":86222,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T17:34:55.000Z","msg":"你會記得佢既氣味，你會知道佢鐘意啲咩，你會知道佢唔鐘意啲咩，會記得幾時係佢生日，會記得佢講既每句說話，會想每分每秒都係同佢過"},{"pid":"5379f37e3877cc043fe36fd9b406faedc123ea4a","